<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Cancellation and Refund Policy | CodeCollab</title>
  <%- include('head-scripts') %>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: white;
    }

    .top-navbar {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      height: 60px;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .navbar-brand {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .policy-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .policy-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .policy-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .last-updated {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .section {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #3b82f6;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .section p, .section li {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .section ul {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .back-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      color: white;
    }

    .highlight-box {
      background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    .warning-box {
      background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    .success-box {
      background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    .refund-timeline {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .timeline-icon {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .timeline-icon.step1 { background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); color: #3b82f6; }
    .timeline-icon.step2 { background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2); color: #8b5cf6; }
    .timeline-icon.step3 { background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2); color: #10b981; }

    .timeline-content h4 {
      margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .timeline-content p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Top Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg top-navbar">
    <div class="container-fluid px-4">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
        <i class="bi bi-code-slash me-2"></i>
        CodeCollab
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="policy-container">
    <a href="/" class="back-link">
      <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i>
      Back to Home
    </a>

    <div class="policy-card">
      <h1 class="policy-title">Cancellation and Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: January 2, 2026</p>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>1. Overview</h2>
        <p>This policy outlines the terms for cancellation and refunds for CodeCollab Pro subscriptions. We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase.</p>
        <div class="highlight-box">
          <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>
          <strong>Digital Service:</strong> CodeCollab is a digital software service. No physical products are shipped.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>2. Subscription Cancellation</h2>
        <p>You can cancel your CodeCollab Pro subscription at any time:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Go to your <strong>Profile Settings</strong></li>
          <li>Click on <strong>Subscription</strong></li>
          <li>Select <strong>Cancel Subscription</strong></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="warning-box">
          <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
          <strong>Important:</strong> After cancellation, you will continue to have Pro access until the end of your current billing period.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>3. Refund Eligibility</h2>
        <p>We offer refunds under the following conditions:</p>
        
        <div class="success-box">
          <h4 style="color: #10b981; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;"><i class="bi bi-check-circle me-2"></i>Eligible for Full Refund</h4>
          <ul style="margin: 0;">
            <li>Request made within <strong>7 days</strong> of purchase</li>
            <li>Technical issues preventing service access</li>
            <li>Duplicate/accidental charges</li>
            <li>Service not as described</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="warning-box">
          <h4 style="color: #f59e0b; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;"><i class="bi bi-x-circle me-2"></i>Not Eligible for Refund</h4>
          <ul style="margin: 0;">
            <li>Request made after 7 days of purchase</li>
            <li>Change of mind after using Pro features</li>
            <li>Account suspended due to Terms violation</li>
            <li>Failure to cancel before renewal</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>4. How to Request a Refund</h2>
        <div class="refund-timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-icon step1">1</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>Contact Support</h4>
              <p>Email us at <strong>codecollabbeta@gmail.com</strong> with subject "Refund Request"</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-icon step2">2</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>Provide Details</h4>
              <p>Include your registered email, payment ID, and reason for refund</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-icon step3">3</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>Receive Refund</h4>
              <p>Approved refunds are processed within 5-7 business days</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>5. Refund Processing</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Processing Time:</strong> 5-7 business days after approval</li>
          <li><strong>Refund Method:</strong> Original payment method (via Razorpay)</li>
          <li><strong>Bank Processing:</strong> Additional 3-5 days depending on your bank</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>6. Pro-rated Refunds</h2>
        <p>We do not offer pro-rated refunds for partial subscription periods. If you cancel mid-cycle:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your Pro access continues until the end of the 3-month billing period</li>
          <li>No refund for unused days</li>
          <li>You won't be charged for the next billing cycle</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>7. Technical Issues</h2>
        <p>If you're experiencing technical issues:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Contact us first at <strong>codecollabbeta@gmail.com</strong></li>
          <li>We'll attempt to resolve the issue within 48 hours</li>
          <li>If unresolved, you're eligible for a full refund</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>8. Chargebacks</h2>
        <p>We encourage you to contact us before initiating a chargeback with your bank. Chargebacks may result in:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Immediate suspension of your account</li>
          <li>Loss of any remaining Pro benefits</li>
          <li>Additional investigation time</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For refund requests or questions about this policy:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> codecollabbeta@gmail.com</p>
        <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 24-48 hours</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
